sources.title: Triple Cross (1966 Thriller) Christopher Plummer | Double Agent. Real Danger. All True! 4K
sources.description:
The true story of Eddie Chapman, ex-safecracker, master-criminal, & super-spy!
During WW2, convicted bank robber Eddie Chapman becomes a triple agent working for both the British and the Germans.

Original title: La Fantastique Histoire Vraie d'Eddie Chapman (France)
Alternative titles: Triple Cross (English), Spion zwischen zwei Fronten (Germany), Agli ordini del Fuhrer e al servizio di Sua Maestà (Italy), Тройной крест (Russia)

Director: Terence Young
Writers: René Hardy, Frank Owen, William Marchant

Main cast:
Christopher Plummer – Eddie Chapman
Romy Schneider – Countess Helga Lindstrom
Yul Brynner – Colonel Baron von Grunen
Trevor Howard – Freddie Young (British Intelligence)
Gert Fröbe – Colonel Steinhäger
Claudine Auger – Paulette

Genres: Action, Adventure, Drama, Thriller, War
Release date: December 9, 1966
